{"tid":1379352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[前線戰術]  layer by layer","createTime":"2019-07-28T18:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T01:11:59.000Z","uid":40720,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5194968e70294b48713aadd3fc2d980675cf9062","tid":1379352,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xejzvdc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXejzvdc.png&h=55f90c11&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的。依家黑警已經係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">依賴</span></strong>左tear gas 去對抗我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而每次一放tear gas，大家就好亂，前線散得好西利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n但對付 tear gas，最緊要係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">空間</span></span>同<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">視野</span></span></strong>，因為如果你發現粒彈係你身邊，你就可以馬上跑過去處理，越遲熄，就越lai西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n但我地咁多次抗爭，好多時候我地都好想big爆個前線，又開曬遮，block 埋視線，<span style=\"color: red;\">even粒彈落左自己身邊都唔知，都睇唔到！</span> 所以消防部應該企開少少，可能每個人之間有2-3m距離，你見到彈係你身邊，就馬上過去熄左佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地都明白有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃金5秒鐘</span></span>，基本上，彈落地後5秒左右，你熄唔到佢，佢已經會散得好西利，一黎你搵唔到佢係邊，二黎你搵到你都會好辛苦。所以我地最好keep 住好嘅空間比我地去撲火。<br />\n<br />\n咁前線咪好危險？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無back up？   如果佢真係放tear gas 後，馬上放速龍，我地就用遠攻 dump 7佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果都係埋到身，就近攻同佢死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而另一方面，前線無咁多人嘅好處，就係前線想退時，有空間比佢地退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，今日係上環有一幕，速龍衝得好&quot;衡&quot;，前排差d人踩人，我見到有女仔係後退時比人撞跌左...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？如果有用嘅話，唔該push 一push"},{"pid":"343779a09b1fd2e3a88a9cbf44dc9f5f76f53bfe","tid":1379352,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:49:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"db7a50dd404e144b8882b5b8afb351aba550fdad","tid":1379352,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:49:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e71b05c67f69c306e1eae5ec42a49ecf6c87b6aa","tid":1379352,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:49:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fc4d6906002c0a9924aeefa6104c1f95c2147f32","tid":1379352,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:49:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e5f1e5a1e52d2c957eab18e14aad814a0d54e448","tid":1379352,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:50:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"97d94fad287d2cec414d76f53d77879057869a81","tid":1379352,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:50:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"57c0ae0c5bda0f5b570bbea916dd36aabcdc41bd","tid":1379352,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:51:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"939bd47dd32dd00276bf36fadd0734b2617db3b5","tid":1379352,"uid":69544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:53:18.000Z","msg":"推，好理想，<br />\n但係實行係一個好大嘅問題，<br />\n發夢見到好撚迫，<br />\n好多消防員衝上去淋同一個彈，<br />\n同埋我半近半遠，啲狗係咁玩遠攻，搞到我無撚曬用。"},{"pid":"52dd6f3d46b12687411758491edb298184ff3132","tid":1379352,"uid":40720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"939bd47dd32dd00276bf36fadd0734b2617db3b5","tid":1379352,"uid":69544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:53:18.000Z","msg":"推，好理想，<br />\n但係實行係一個好大嘅問題，<br />\n發夢見到好撚迫，<br />\n好多消防員衝上去淋同一個彈，<br />\n同埋我半近半遠，啲狗係咁玩遠攻，搞到我無撚曬用。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:56:36.000Z","msg":"1.半近半遠就係做消防post 就岩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.其實2-3 個有水嘅消防去整同一粒彈都夠曬<br />\n3. 所以就係大家前排其實唔洗企咁close"},{"pid":"0a6b3540c2bc8663519f36f023f9cba3aca8376f","tid":1379352,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:57:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80f5220f945ce1d8bad4387abbd27ef065839b6c","tid":1379352,"uid":124824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db8ca6299d5195f082bb1639bd095e491aeb1ca","tid":1379352,"uid":269428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}